text:
Sorry for keeping you waiting, Yuika──
......?
...What, are you planning to throw that snowball at me...?

You've got to be kidding me, Producer...!
What do you think these cute leaf-shaped ears are for...!?

Besides, it's clearly not spherical at all.
If it was meant to be a snowball, I'd make it round!
Yuika's not that clumsy, you know.
